MonoBehaviour.m_text:
"Your mom asked you to go to the villages market today to buy meat. Shegave you money, but you bought candy instead. When you go back home, she willask you "Did you buy meat?". If you are empty-handed, she will ground you fora week. So now you have to get creative at the villages market.

The game ends when you get the meat. 
Hint: Try first by exchanging some products you  obtain. 
During the game, press "h" for more hints. 
Good luck!"
